description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 2-bed, 1-bath residence offers a bright and sun-filled living space. Spacious primary bedroom easily fits a king bed, while the versatile second bedroom works perfectly as a home office or can accommodate a full-sized bed. The full bath features an in-unit stackable washer/dryer for ultimate convenience. Take in sweeping city views from the shared rooftop deck, the perfect spot to relax or entertain. All this just minutes from the Broadway T, plus neighborhood restaurants, cafes, and shops right at your doorstep.
